data.description: Embrace the New Year in style with our charming townhome in Helena! Nestled in a tranquil cil-de-sac behind Penhale Park, this residence offers one level living convenience with main-level bedroom and bathroom. The upstairs features and additional bedroom and bathroom, ideal for roommates or family.  Ample storage awaits with closets galore, attic space, and outdoor storage for your gardening essentials. As the coveted end unit, relish the peace and quiet of this hidden gem.  Kickstart your new year with this amazing find, perfectly situated for easy access to Helena, Pelham, and the sought-after Alabaster School system.
